Date: Sat, 24 Jan 2026 08:21:30 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 06/18] Add jump rendering infrastructure to connector DOM
 renderer

- Create createConnectorPathWithJumps function with all 5 jump styles
  * arc: Curved bezier arc over intersection
  * sharp: Angular jump perpendicular to line
  * gap: Discontinuity in line
  * line: Crossing X shape
  * none: Straight through (no jump)
- Add jump style support to connectorBaseDomRenderer
- Extract jumpStyle and jumpSize from model properties
- Add detailed TODO for wiring up intersection detection

Jump rendering function ready - awaits view layer integration
to access all connectors for intersection calculation.

Based on draw.io's jump rendering (Graph.js:9161-9292).

Phase 4 complete - rendering infrastructure in place.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
